<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather:300,700,300italic,700italic|Source+Sans+Pro:900');

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            background-color: #2a2f4a;
            background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?q=80&w=2072&auto=format&fit=crop'); 
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 2;
            color: #212931;
            padding-top: 4rem; 
        }

        #wrapper {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 72rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        #header {
            border-bottom: solid 2px #eeeeee;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 4rem 2rem 4rem;
        }
        #header h1 {
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.075em;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        #main {
            padding: 4rem;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.075em;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: solid 2px #212931;
            color: #212931;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-block;
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 0.25em;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            line-height: 3.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            white-space: nowrap;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #212931;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        #footer {
            padding: 4rem;
            border-top: solid 2px #eeeeee;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.25em;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #717981;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 736px) {
            body { padding-top: 2rem; }
            #header, #main, #footer { padding: 2rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="wrapper">
        <header id="header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        </header>
        <div id="main">
            <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> March 3, 2026</p>

            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect information you provide directly to us. This includes your name, email address, and phone number when you request a quote, fill out a contact form, or initiate a phone call to our business lines.</p>

            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services. Specifically, your phone number will be used to send automated text messages related strictly to your customer service inquiries, estimates, and appointment bookings.</p>

            <h2>3. Information Sharing and SMS Consent</h2>
            <p>We take your privacy seriously. <strong>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information, including your mobile phone number, with third parties or affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes.</strong> All text messaging originator opt-in data and consent details will remain strictly confidential and will not be shared with any third parties.</p>

            <h2>4. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at: okayjerd@gmail.com.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="index.html" class="button">Return to Homepage</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <footer id="footer">
            &copy; 2026 OkayJerd.
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
